These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: milk, soy-milk, almond-milk, iced-tea
Sport: biathlon, baseball, skateboarding, rowing
1. Beverage:milk is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1
2. Sport:rowing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:skateboarding is between Sport:baseball and Beverage:soy-milk##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk is between Beverage:soy-milk and Beverage:milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea         | soy-milk   | almond-milk | milk       |
| Sport      | rowing | biathlon | skateboarding   | baseball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: board-games, traveling, woodworking, dancing
Nationality: nigerian, argentine, spanish, french
1. Nationality:french is between Hobby:woodworking and Nationality:argentine##2
2. Hobby:dancing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:spanish is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
4. Hobby:board-games is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | traveling | board-games | woodworking | dancing |
| Nationality   | argentine    | french   | nigerian | spanish       |

