3. Nationality:brazilian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:chinese is on the left of Food:pomegranate##1
5. Food:cabbage == Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | watermelon    | orange | cabbage   | pomegranate  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian   | chinese | indian |

